descript.abstract: Levee segments for the Sacramento River System. All alignments extracted from California Levee Database (CaLD), provided by PBSJ, unless noted in the "SRC_CMMNTS" field in the attribute table. Levee Units/Segments based on Operation and Maintenance (OM) Manual Maps and Plat maps provided by PBSJ (which were created from the OM maps by DWR and provided to PBSJ by USACE). For information about the levee alignments, please see the documentation for the CaLD. The segments (start and end points) are based on the best resolution the reference imagery (scanned and georeferenced OM Manual Maps and PBSJ provided Plat maps) allows. Levee line gaps, kinks and other misalignments were corrected according to a digitized KML file provided by W. Daniel Meyersohn of DWR and verified using 2005 NAIP imagery. Please note that while misalignments were corrected, the associated elevations for these misalignments have not likewise been corrected. This effort will be completed at a later date based on Survey and/or LiDAR data.
descript.purpose: Provide reference between CaLD and Operation and Maintenance Manuals.
